trans-unit.source: Defines a polygon-shaped hot spot region in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en polygon-formet hot sted område i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: This class defines a polygon-shaped hot spot region in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen definerer et område for polygon-formet hot sted i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: The PolygonHotSpot is useful for defining irregularly shaped hot spot regions in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control.
trans-unit.target: PolygonHotSpot er nyttig for definerer uvanlig formet e-områder i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can use it to define individual regions within a geographical map.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel bruke den til å definere individuelle områder i et geografiske kart.

trans-unit.source: To define the region of a PolygonHotSpot, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot.Coordinates%2A> property to a string that specifies the coordinates of each vertex of the PolygonHotSpot object.
trans-unit.target: For å angi området for en PolygonHotSpot er angitt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot.Coordinates%2A>egenskapen til en streng som angir koordinatene til hver toppunkt i PolygonHotSpot-objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot.Coordinates%2A>

trans-unit.source: A polygon vertex is a point at which two polygon edges meet.
trans-unit.target: Et polygon toppunkt er et punkt som oppfyller to polygon kanter.

trans-unit.source: When a PolygonHotSpot object is clicked, the page navigates to a URL, generates a post back to the server, or does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Når et objekt for PolygonHotSpot, siden navigerer til en URL-adresse, genererer en post på serveren, eller gjøre noe.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property specifies this behavior.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen angir dette problemet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To navigate to a URL, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.Navigate`, and use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A> property to specify the URL to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil navigere til en URL-adresse, kan du angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen `HotSpotMode.Navigate`, og bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A>til å angi URL-adressen til å navigere til.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.NavigateUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To post back to the server, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.PostBack`, and use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> property to specify a name for the PolygonHotSpot object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til serveren, kan du angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen `HotSpotMode.PostBack`, og bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>til å angi et navn for PolygonHotSpot-objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: This name will be passed in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs> event data when the PolygonHotSpot is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Dette navnet vil bli sendt i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>Hendelsesdata når PolygonHotSpot klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMapEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: If you want the PolygonHotSpot object to have no behavior, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A> property to `HotSpotMode.Inactive`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil PolygonHotSpot-objektet har ingen virkemåte, angitt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>egenskapen `HotSpotMode.Inactive`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å initialisere en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: A string of coordinates that represents the vertexes of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: En streng med koordinater som representerer toppunkt for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Use the Coordinates property to specify the coordinates of the vertexes of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk egenskapen koordinatene til å angi koordinatene toppunkt for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: A polygon vertex is a point at which two polygon edges meet.
trans-unit.target: Et polygon toppunkt er et punkt som oppfyller to polygon kanter.

trans-unit.source: The string that you specify must be formatted with each coordinate separated by a comma.
trans-unit.target: Strengen som du angir må formateres med hver koordinaten atskilt med semikolon.

trans-unit.source: Each vertex that you specify must have both an x- coordinate and a y-coordinate.
trans-unit.target: Hvert toppunkt som du angir må ha både en x-koordinaten og y-koordinat.

trans-unit.source: For example, the string "128,185,335,157,510,224,510,383,228,383" defines a polygon hot spot with five vertexes.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel definerer strengen "128,185,335,157,510,224,510,383,228,383" et polygon hot merke med fem toppunkt.

trans-unit.source: The x-coordinate of the first vertex is 128.
trans-unit.target: X-koordinaten for første ytterpunktet er 128.

trans-unit.source: The y-coordinate of the first vertex is 185.
trans-unit.target: Y-koordinaten for første ytterpunktet er 185.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the coordinates of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"></xref> object's vertexes.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer koordinatene til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"> </xref> objektets toppunkt.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string that represents the coordinates of the vertexes of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en streng som representerer koordinatene toppunkt for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The GetCoordinates method returns a string that represents the coordinates of the vertexes of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetCoordinates returnerer en streng som representerer koordinatene toppunkt for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The string this method returns is the current value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot.Coordinates%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Strengen metoden returnerer er gjeldende verdi for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot.Coordinates%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot.Coordinates%2A>

trans-unit.source: The GetCoordinates method is used internally by ASP.NET to get the text to use for the coordinates of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot> when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetCoordinates brukes internt ASP.NET teksten skal brukes for koordinatene til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>når den gjengis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The string that is returned is specific to the browser and markup language.
trans-unit.target: Strengen som returneres er spesifikk for nettleseren og markup language.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the coordinates of the vertexes of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer koordinatene toppunkt for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.
